summary: Completed comprehensive testing of admin panel new features: admin password change and plans CRUD operations. All backend APIs working correctly (26/27 tests passed). Frontend UI fully functional with proper integration between admin panel and landing page dynamic plan loading.

minor_issues.issue: Test expects 403 on 3rd record creation, but user was upgraded to 'pro' plan during testing
minor_issues.impact: Test logic issue, not application bug - user has higher limits after plan upgrade

ui_warnings.issue: Console warnings about missing Description for DialogContent

passed_tests: User login with new password after admin change
Admin plans CRUD operations (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE /api/admin/plans/*)
Public plans API returns data from MongoDB (GET /api/plans)
Landing page loads plans dynamically from database
Admin panel navigation (Users, Records, Plans, Settings tabs)
Password change dialog UI (accessible via key icon)
Frontend-backend integration for all admin features
Dynamic plan loading on landing page (4 plans displayed including created ones)
All existing features continue to work (auth, DNS records, user management)
